30
00:02:24,729 --> 00:02:28,541
Alice had learnt several things of this sort in her lessons in the schoolroom,
爱丽丝在学校教室里学过一些这类的东西，

31
00:02:28,541 --> 00:02:34,831
and though this was not a _very_ good opportunity for showing off her knowledge, as there was no one to listen to her,
虽然这不是一个展示她知识的好机会，因为没有人听她说话，

